{
  "stem": "1918.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 405.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's supposed to be some kind of happy music-- I don't remember what it was-- and they're playing some very tragic music, something that sounded like probably Beethoven or something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember what the piece was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she had a very definite sense that something is wrong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then it passed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were all these friends around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were having a good time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Monday morning on the 20th, very early in the morning, somebody knocked on the window and said, it's me, [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Shani, ?] or [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Lotzi, ?] whatever his Hungarian name was, one of the friends my brother had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he went to school in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he says, let me in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Let me in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we let him in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he told us this horrible story of the Nazis marched in Sunday afternoon-- which of course they did not announce on the radio right then-- when my sister sensed it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he said that they came into the school, and people were starting to run through the windows and throwing chairs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he managed in this madness, in this-- it was absolutely awful, he said.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was such fear, such terror everywhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he made his way to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he will-- he came to our house, and he will go back to his village to his parents-- which they lived a few miles away-- right after he's talking to us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He told us this horrible Sunday that he lived through in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he went back to his parents, and we never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But by then, Monday morning, it was quite obvious that they marched in.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
